description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Asian elephant in Kanchanaburi, Thailand
-Bighorn sheep in Jasper National Park, Canada
-Emperor penguins and seals in Antarctica
-Sheeps Lofoten islands, Norway
-Giraffes in Tsavo National Park, Kenya
-Cows in the Bernese Oberland, Switzerland
-Polar bear in the Arctic
-Monkeys at a natural hot spring in Japan
-Stingrays on Maldives beach
-Giant Turtle in the Galapagos Islands
name: Wildlife in the Spotlight
